==Korean==

===Noun===
'''숨''' (sum) cf. [[sum]] 
# [[breath]]  
# [[liveliness]], [[spirit]], [[vigor]]
 
====Derived terms====
'''Prefix to nouns'''
*숨[[결]] (-gyeol) the state of breathing 
*숨[[구멍]] (-gumeong) [[throat]], [[windpipe]], [[trachea]] 
*숨[[소리]] (-sori) the sound of breathing 
*숨[[통]] (-tong) [[throat]], [[windpipe]], [[trachea]] 

'''Suffix to nouns'''
*[[단]]숨에 (dan-sum-e) [[in one breath]] cf. 한숨 (Either literally means ''one breath''.)
*[[목]]숨 (mog-, mok-) [[life]]
*[[한]]숨 (han-) one breath, [[pause]], [[sigh]] 

'''Prefix to verbs'''
*숨[[가쁘다]] (-gappeuda)  to be [[out of breath]] 
*숨[[거두다]] (-geoduda) to [[breathe one's last]] 
*숨[[넘어가다]] (-neomEogada) to [[breathe one's last]] 
*숨[[돌리다]] (-dollida) to [[take breath]]
*숨[[막히다]] (-maghida, -makhida) to be [[choked]], [[suffocated]] 
*숨[[쉬다]] (-swida) to [[breathe]]
*숨[[죽이다]] (-jugIda) to [[hold one's breath]], [[wither]] (vegetables, etc.) 
*숨[[지다]] (-jida) to [[breathe]] one's last]], [[die]] 
*숨[[차다]] (-chada) to be [[out of breath]]  

